content: We (@AbdulMalik Shakir and I) are getting an error (http://build.fhir.org/ig/HL7/vrdr/branches/master/build.log) when running IG Publisher on this STU3 IG. The only thing that's changed since it went to ballot in March is the ig.json FHIR version (3.0.1 -> 3.0.2) and the implementation guide resource fhir version (3.0.1 -> 3.0.2). Any ideas on how to fix this?
Never mind, scrapping this IG and overwriting most of the files...
